All requests are submitted via POST to URL /api1
All responses are sent as json objects

1. Generate password 

   request

      operation=genpass
      login=<phone_number>

      operation=gen_pass&login=9211234567

   response

       Success

          Error    0
          ErrorMsg ""
 
       Failure

          Error = N
          ErrorMsg = "Error message"

2. Authenticate

   request

      operation=auth
      login=<phone_number>
      pass=<password>

      operation=auth&login=9211234567&pass=12345

   response

      none (redirected to hotspot)
